tika-abh09t2:2_0: Saṅgaho asaṅgaho (dhātu. 1). Saṅgahitena asaṅgahitaṁ. Asaṅgahitena saṅgahitaṁ. Saṅgahitena
tika-abh09t2:2_1: saṅgahitaṁ. Asaṅgahitena asaṅgahitaṁ. Sampayogo vippayogo. Sampayuttena vippayuttaṁ.
tika-abh09t2:2_2: Vippayuttena sampayuttaṁ. Sampayuttena sampayuttaṁ. Vippayuttena vippayuttaṁ. Saṅgahitena
tika-abh09t2:2_3: sampayuttaṁ vippayuttaṁ. Sampayuttena saṅgahitaṁ asaṅgahitaṁ. Asaṅgahitena sampayuttaṁ
tika-abh09t2:4_0: Pañcakkhandhā. Dvādasāyatanāni. Aṭṭhārasa dhātuyo. Cattāri saccāni. Bāvīsatindriyāni.
tika-abh09t2:4_1: Paṭiccasamuppādo. Cattāro satipaṭṭhānā. Cattāro sammappadhānā. Cattāro iddhipādā
tika-abh09t2:4_2: . Cattāri jhānāni. Catasso appamaññāyo. Pañcindriyāni. Pañca balāni. Satta bojjhaṅgā.
tika-abh09t2:4_3: Ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo. Phasso vedanā saññā cetanā cittaṁ adhimokkho manasikāro.
tika-abh09t2:6: Tīhi saṅgaho. Tīhi asaṅgaho. Catūhi sampayogo. Catūhi vippayogo.
